<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent0cbd3b74872b468cb59c580584cc7eda">
</div>
<p>Rowley Hall Hospital is one of the leading <a href="http://www.rowleyhallhospital.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Private hosptial in Staffordshire">private hospitals in Staffordshire </a>with an excellent reputation for delivering high quality healthcare for self pay/insured and NHS patients. It is located in a Georgian listed building in five acres of Rowley Park, only five minutes from the centre of Stafford. The hospital opened in 1987 and currently has 14 bedrooms all with en suite facilities.</p>
<p>Our key surgeries include <a href="http://www.rowleyhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/cosmetic-surgery">cosmetic surgery</a>, <a href="http://www.rowleyhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/spine-and-neck-care">spine and neck surgery</a>, <a href="http://www.rowleyhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/lens-exchange-surgery">eye surgery</a> and <a href="http://www.rowleyhallhospital.co.uk/treatment/orthopaedics">orthopaedic surgery</a>.</p>
<p><br/>By investing in advanced medical technology, the hospital offers a wide range of <a href="http://www.rowleyhallhospital.co.uk/treatments/treatments-and-services.aspx" target="_blank" title="Treatments at Rowley Hall">treatments.</a> Please click the <a href="/Services/hospitals/Services/DefaultView.aspx?id=704" target="_self" title="Choose and book services">departments and services</a> for treatments available on Choose and Book.</p>
<p>The fully equipped ultra clean air operating theatre has laminar air flow. This is particularly suitable for Orthopaedic surgery such as arthroscopy, hip and knee replacements and spinal surgery.</p>
<p>We have excellent levels of cleanliness and have effective infection control methods resulting in very low infection rates. All our facilities are regularly inspected and approved by the Care Quality Commission.</p>
<p>Free car parking and disabled access is also available.</p>
<p>Our consultants and nursing staff are highly experienced and have your care and comfort as their highest priority. During and after treatment, you will receive a standard of care which is second to none and all patients have the reassurance that theatre, paramedical services and a resident RMO is available 24 hours a day.</p>
